            // Idle mode detailed info
            { "DetailedInfo0", "\U0001F3AE Simple \u2014 Parallel Idle\n\nThe simplest mode. Launches the selected number of games\nsimultaneously. Steam sees them as running and accumulates\nplay time for each of them.\n\n\u2022 Max 32 games simultaneously (Steam limitation)\n\u2022 Set a time limit or run indefinitely\n\u2022 All games start and stop together\n\nRecommended for quickly accumulating hours across several games." },
            { "DetailedInfo1", "\U0001F4CB Sequential \u2014 One by One\n\nLaunches games strictly one at a time. When one game\nhas run for the specified duration, it closes and\nthe next one from the list starts automatically.\n\n\u2022 One game at a time\n\u2022 Set hours per game\n\u2022 Processes the entire displayed game list\n\nRecommended when you need to accumulate many hours\nin specific games sequentially." },
            { "DetailedInfo2", "\U0001F504 Round-Robin \u2014 Rotation\n\nCyclic rotation in batches. The first batch of games\n(up to 32) is launched, after the set interval it stops\nand the next batch starts. When all batches are done,\nthe cycle starts over.\n\n\u2022 Rotation interval is configurable (5-1440 min)\n\u2022 Each batch \u2014 up to 32 games\n\u2022 Runs indefinitely or for a set time\n\nIdeal for cycling through hundreds of games in one session,\ndistributing hours evenly." },
            { "DetailedInfo3", "\U0001F3AF Target Hours \u2014 Until Target\n\nLaunches a batch of games (up to 32 simultaneously) and runs\nfor the specified number of hours. When time is up,\nthe current batch stops and the next batch starts.\nContinues until all games in the list reach target hours.\n\n\u2022 Batches of N games (configurable, max 32)\n\u2022 Automatic batch switching\n\u2022 Single-pass: each game is processed once\n\nRecommended for mass hour accumulation across all games." },
            { "DetailedInfo4", "\U0001F550 Schedule \u2014 Time Window\n\nIdle runs only within a specified time window.\nOutside the schedule, processes are automatically paused,\nand resumed when the window starts.\n\n\u2022 Set start and end time (HH:MM)\n\u2022 Supports overnight windows (e.g., 23:00 \u2014 07:00)\n\u2022 Number of games and hours are configurable\n\nRecommended for unattended idle (overnight, when away from PC)." },
            { "DetailedInfo5", "\U0001F6E1 Anti-Idle \u2014 Detection Evasion\n\nPeriodic restart of all processes.\nEvery N minutes all idle processes are killed\nand restarted. This simulates natural behavior\n(launching/exiting games).\n\n\u2022 Restart interval is configurable (10-1440 min)\n\u2022 Runs indefinitely or for a set time\n\u2022 Creates a more natural activity pattern\n\nRecommended for extended idle sessions (12+ hours)." },

